[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24893155","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4912#issuecomment-24893155","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4912","id":24893155,"user":{"login":"bantu","id":189375,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fcdc48f189c0e2e8a870f3d54615a2f0d.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu","html_url":"https://github.com/bantu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-22t23:26:07z","updated_at":"2013-09-22t23:28:57z","body":"many users of `delete()` in `./lib/public/share.php`. some of those should probably also use `unshare()`.\r\n\r\n```shell\r\nafischer@leonard:/var/www/projects/owncloud/core (fix-link-expiration) $ grep \"self::delete\" . -ri\r\n...\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\tself::delete($row['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\t\tself::delete($checkexists['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\tself::delete($item['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\tself::delete($share['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\tself::delete($item['id'], true, \\oc_user::getuser());\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\tself::delete($item['id'], true);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\tself::delete($item['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\t\tself::delete($item['id'], true);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\t\tself::delete($row['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\tself::delete($item['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\tself::delete($item['id'], true, $arguments['uid']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\t\tself::delete($item['id']);\r\n./lib/public/share.php:\t\t\tself::delete($item['id']);\r\n...\r\n```"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24893348","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4912#issuecomment-24893348","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4912","id":24893348,"user":{"login":"bantu","id":189375,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fcdc48f189c0e2e8a870f3d54615a2f0d.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu","html_url":"https://github.com/bantu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-22t23:37:42z","updated_at":"2013-09-22t23:37:42z","body":"users of `delete()` in `./lib/public/share.php` on `fix-link-expiration` are:\r\n```shell\r\ngetsharebytoken() when share is expired\r\nshareitem() when updating a link share\r\nunshare()\r\nunshareall()\r\nunsharefromself()\r\nsetpermissions() when share permissions are removed\r\ngetitems() when share is expired\r\npost_deleteuser()\r\npost_removefromgroup()\r\n```\r\n\r\naccording to https://github.com/owncloud/core/pull/4856/files#r6436470 `getsharebytoken()` and `getitems()` should use `unshare()` instead of `delete()`.\r\n\r\nthis leaves the following candidates:\r\n```shell\r\nshareitem() when updating a link share\r\nunshareall()\r\nunsharefromself()\r\nsetpermissions() when share permissions are removed\r\npost_deleteuser()\r\npost_removefromgroup()\r\n```\r\n\r\n@schiesbn which of these should use `unshare()` instead of `delete()`?"},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24908182","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4912#issuecomment-24908182","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4912","id":24908182,"user":{"login":"schiesbn","id":1589737,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2f0a323047dbe8329db30eae8dbe96e55e.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"8912b598c7b32dd25b87fd168e0b06b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn","html_url":"https://github.com/schiesbn","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/schiesbn/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-23t09:36:06z","updated_at":"2013-09-23t09:37:15z","body":"@bantu we should use unshare() everywhere where the file is really unshared (permanently) to allow other apps to get notified and to react on it.\r\n\r\nwe shouldn't change it where delete() is used just as a intermediate step like here: https://github.com/owncloud/core/blob/master/lib/public/share.php#l455 because in this case it is not a unshare operation but a update, performed as a delete() followed by a put(). btw. this also create other issues, e.g. the share id changes just because the password was updated. we should fix this to update the database directly instead of removing the item and adding it again.\r\n\r\ntl;dr every delete() which performs a permanent unshare() should call unshare() instead of delete(). if we find examples where delete() is just a intermediate step for a different operation we should try to get rid of the delete() completely and perform the db update directly."},{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/comments/24911582","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/4912#issuecomment-24911582","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/4912","id":24911582,"user":{"login":"bantu","id":189375,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fcdc48f189c0e2e8a870f3d54615a2f0d.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"88483d87947219efecfc570465c753b2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu","html_url":"https://github.com/bantu","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/bantu/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"created_at":"2013-09-23t